Enum Class CharacterOptions

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CharacterOptions>
project.chenlin_17.tools.CharacterOptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CharacterOptions>, Constable
public enum CharacterOptions extends Enum<CharacterOptions>
Each constructor set have its defined value for character image and paddle image, since they are designed to bind with each other.
The player is able to set the paddle image by choosing the character
